			(property "Description" "The CM108B is a highly integrated single-chip USB audio solution. All essential analog modules are embedded in the CM108B, including dual DAC and earphone driver, ADC, microphone booster, PLL, regulator and USB transceiver modules. It is perfectly suited to USB headset, USB earphone or USB audio-interface box applications. As well, many features are programmable with jumper pins or by external EEPROM."
